Insider Activity


Individual




Vernon J. Nagel



Mr. Vernon J. Nagel, CPA, is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Acuity Brands, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Holophane Corp., a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants, and President & Chief Executive Officer at Acuity Brands Lighting, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at National Electrical Manufacturers Association and Georgia Aquarium, Inc.
Mr. Nagel was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer, Secretary, Treasurer & VP by Stericycle, Inc., Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & Executive VP by Kuhlman Corp., and a Principal by Jepson Associates, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Michigan.



