Vernon J. Nagel 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman, President and Chief Executive Officer at ACUITY BRANDS INC, Vernon J. Nagel  made $10,659,517 in total compensation.  Of this total $600,000 was received as a salary, $5,000,000 was received as a bonus, $1,666,681 was received in stock options, $3,333,320 was awarded as stock and $59,516 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


